title: 'Fantastic human' Russo shines in Arsenal win at Everton
subtitle: England striker Alessia Russo was at the heart of Arsenal's WSL win at Everton - a reminder to doubters of how indispensable she is.
full_text: England striker Alessia Russo was at the heart of Arsenal's WSL win at Everton - a reminder to doubters of how indispensable she is.
